HKLM | HKU | HKCU | HKCC | HKCR
HKLM - Boot/Hardware info
  Subkeys - Hardware | SAM | Security | System
HKU - All User Profiles in System w/ different SIDs
    - Env Settings | Shortcuts | file assoc
    - S-1-5-18 | S-1-5-19 | S-1-5-20 | S-1-5-21
HKCU - Copy of users' registry based on SID 
HKCC - Symbolic Link to HKLM/Key/Subkey/Subkey/Subkey
HKCR - Symbolic Link to HKLM/Key/Subkey
     - File extension associations and COM reg info
*Root keys stored on disk
HIVE ON DISKS - SAM | SECURITY | SOFTWARE | SYSTEM | HARDWARE | .DEFAULT | <SID> | <SID>_CLASSES
*Hives stored in %SYSTEMROOT%\System32\config
HKLM\Hardware - dynamic in memory each boot
HKU\<SID> - in %USERPROFILE%\NTUSER.DAT
HKU\<SID>_CLASSES - in %USERPROFILE%\Application Data\Local\Microsoft\Windows\UsrClass.dat
Hive File Extensions - .alt | .log | .sav
Get-ChildItem - List all subkeys/contents
get-item - List contents of reg key/subkey
